Conditional Statements allows us to control the execution flow of code based on some conditions.

They are of two types:- 1. If statements  2. CASE Statements

1. If are further of 3 types.
  i). If then.
  ii). If then else.
  iii). If then elseif.
  
2. Case statements
  i). Simple Case.
  ii). Searched Case.
